 der Ideentheorie. Die Forschung zu diesem platonischen Dialog hat in den letzten Jahren eine neue Dynamik bekommen, die sich in dem vorliegenden Band spiegelt, der in Form eines kooperativen Kommentars 12 Originalbeiträge international renommierter Philosophen vereint. MIT BEITRÄGEN VON: Pierre Destrée, Dorothea Frede, Christoph Horn, Nora Kreft, Bernd Manuwald, Jörn Müller, Christian Pietsch, C. D. C. Reeve, Frisbee Sheffield, Kurt Sier, Simon Weber und Jula Wildberger.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aDestrée, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrede, Dorothea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHorn, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHorn, Christoph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKreft, Nora, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aManuwald, Bernd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMüller, Jörn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPietsch, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReeve, C. D. C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSheffield, Frisbee, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSier, Kurt, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeber, Simon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWildberger, Jula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket AV  Philos